Package: coreqmapr
Type: Package
Title: Post-processing For Lake Sediment Core Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "William", "Chapman",
      email = "william.m.chapman@mail.mcgill.ca",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides an interface to adjust downcore predicted values of
  modelled lake sediment characteristics using known values at the top of the 
  core. Implements techniques similar to Empirical Quantile Mapping (EQM) and
  Quantile Delta Mapping (QDM) to adjust downcore predictions probabilistically.
